snippet.title: Plug n Play Games: Scooby-Doo and the Mystery of the Castle
snippet.description:
Help support the channel: https://www.patreon.com/ZCInfinity
Review: http://zc-infinity.blogspot.com/2016/10/plug-n-play-game-corner-scooby-doo-and.html

HAPPY HALLOWEEN! Let's celebrate with one of the greatest staples of Halloween: Scooby-Doo!

And sorry for the video quality. My video capture device hates games with fast action. I've bought a new one and, hopefully, that won't happen again.
